case.name: Favorite Plants
case.description: Sucrose is curious what people's favorite plants are. This could be flowers, or something they smoke, etc.

case.name: Introductions
case.description: Sucrose introduces herself and expects the table to do so! You can respond to this, but there's a line for each of Sucrose's hands.

case.name: Lingerie
case.description: Sucrose is more than happy to get comments on her lingerie. For a shy woman, it's certainly something!

case.name: Collaboration on Masturbation
case.description: If Sucrose is finished, she'll offer advice to a female character whose crotch is about to be revealed.

case.name: How do you...
case.description: Sucrose will ask the table how they normally prefer to masturbate if she's not the only one masturbating.

case.name: Euphemisms
case.description: After completing her forfeit, Sucrose may inquire a bit about sexual euphemisms.

case.name: Thong talk
case.description: If another character at the table with a thong is exposed, Sucrose will ask a few questions. Good chance to butt pose!

case.name: Sucrose Ears
case.description: Sucrose's floofy parts of her head are in fact ears, and not just hair...
